title: Valley First Wine Festival
description:
The most anticipated wine event of the Fall season held at the Rotary Centre for the Arts in Kelowna.
Cover2Cover will take the stage and rock the room!
Come enjoy amazing wine and bring your dancing shoes! Tickets are $109 and include unlimited wine and food.
